'''Tipald''' was a [[Netherese]] [[arcanist]] and [[spell]] inventor who lived during the [[Golden Age]].
document_data.History: Tipald developed two spells in their lifetime. The spells they developed were ''[[explosive runes]]'' in {{YearlinkConvert|2108|NY}}, and ''[[conjure elemental]]'' in {{YearlinkConvert|2131|NY}}.
